Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，什麼都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚沒睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保跟清水老師\N竟然是那種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保你太令人羨慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師不是結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保也不可能是她老公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和有夫之婦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是有夫之婦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜夜春宵的有夫之婦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早不要看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有夫之婦指的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟男人結了婚的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是做早操的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先從手部運動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼絲茉茉會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我保管，拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人果然很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的，搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘後要出門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是做這種事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時會早到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她從來沒遲到過的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師到最後還是沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那傢伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個到底在搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我要這個跟這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過新保那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛又要託我保管絲茉茉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，手，手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改變時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為棒球比賽轉播
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預定錄影的節目\N被延後三十分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改變設定時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之回背包裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，那台電腦是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保不知道什麼時候\N偷放到我的背包裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要我幫他保管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，幹嘛要我保管呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既不會成為包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會妨礙到他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但方便、漂亮\N還什麼都會替你做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦真的有很多好處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該對裕美發牢騷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你願意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管牢騷還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都全年無休，照單全收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是新保那傢伙害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請趕快接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請趕快接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再響五聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會轉到答錄機模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個聲音，你是新保對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老師私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是把這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來，快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有影像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快出來，快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，這邊才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，自己接好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師我很高興喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯什麼嗯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私奔是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟清水老師現在私奔中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在問你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛跟補習班老師私奔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候\N跟她開始交往的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經快半年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是\N剛到補習班上課的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在我不注意時跟老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我說了也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼重要的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台電視不但是舊型  又便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接的方法一定也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒時間煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在必須…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，我去稔家裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要乖乖看家喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是“私奔”？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是壞事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道\N該怎麼回答才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補習班學生竟然跟老師私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保這個大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和少爺來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼晚了，發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去準備本須和少爺的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真誇張的出場方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託將她接到有畫面的電話線上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指超高速通信線路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟誰通電話呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞私奔的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫面會出現在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上會出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，你在國分寺家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續剛剛的話題，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先跟你說也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是把你當作朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也當你是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為多香子不同意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多香子已經結婚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次在我那邊過夜的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚之後馬上就迷上電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻間的談話\N變得都是電腦的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子以為他只是\N剛買了電腦高興過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以也沒在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一段時間之後\N她丈夫就只跟電腦說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管多香子在不在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只跟電腦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對電腦不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概想不通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近這種人一直在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得電腦比較可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和人類比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟電腦在一起比較快樂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些話就是指這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離補習班不遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個小公園對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是剛到補習班的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我經過那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候還是叫她清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時老師她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在鞦韆上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為她只是童心大發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩玩鞦韆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我吃完晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻還在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為門鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳忘了帶鑰匙了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙我是有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是上了門鍊，打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門鍊是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很久沒有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連話都說不上兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好罵他幾句不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她搖了搖頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了門鍊就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公忘了我會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不在家都沒影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得怎樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎樣都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在說這麼傷心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻沒有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其實很想哭出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是拼命在忍耐罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少讓她在遇到\N不愉快或傷心的事時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠哭個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後我就窮追不捨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子認為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是補習班學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是補習班老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且已經結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我說了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直追，一直追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就變成了今天這個局面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，為什麼要私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道只剩這個方法了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們這個年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許就如同你所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是我的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得不相信男性的人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她認為就算一開始說喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出現像電腦那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會完全改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像從沒喜歡過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她說過我是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不管說幾次她還是不信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次多香子到本須和房間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算兩人好好談談的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談談關於我們的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過事到臨頭\N她好像還是害怕了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人的心還真是難懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓她跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定私奔到深山的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣濕答答的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩愛愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說，這算是私奔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多香子點頭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:17:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉再幫我保管一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫你保管當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟誰在通電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟本須和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比平常性感好幾倍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜囉，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再跟你聯絡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過或許我可以幫上什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，新保這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果只能當個商量的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，還是在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是到本須和房間去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我找了一個晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我鬧得很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄得他很疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像很睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎是無意識狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我試著問了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經結婚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能喜歡上別人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上一個人，是無法抗拒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對自己的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喜歡上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有對自己都是痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在其中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己覺得自在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然說得出這種大道理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明還是在室男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過不知為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心裡像是放下一塊大石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己覺得自在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到他這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了更輕鬆自在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要到我身邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒，就是表示快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是無憂無慮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還叫我新保啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼問題來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳猜猜\N我一直想要妳怎麼叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿弘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是個好人，本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖是好人卻沒有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷上電腦的丈夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算讓女孩流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是覺得電腦比較好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.11,0:23:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:23:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:23:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.65,0:23:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多加努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要更努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.82,0:24:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更更要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.26,0:24:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，煮飯」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咕嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我肚子發出的聲音
